{"tid":411173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何乙己","createTime":"2017-09-23T14:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T17:30:19.000Z","uid":19408,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10ce5df72bdbd0e077fc6779fa89cf3acdf41f22","tid":411173,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又報了假學歷了！」何君堯睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你讀的學院沒你的名，親自說。」何君堯便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「無執業不能算假&hellip;&hellip;執業！&hellip;&hellip;法律人的事，能算假麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「黃色恐怖」，什麼「欺凌」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"35f6d7cb2d584dd435ea2e1759897c8aad8b4bb6","tid":411173,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab257f88ba3e8ee56e579508bd6f9edeceb4f45f","tid":411173,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b4268bfc8ac15d6c4e0e0e8d81d84f58563756","tid":411173,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de783a750098e52c2aabed46c8cb2df99b66d32","tid":411173,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97ba5e58890a84be13579fff26d5a3002c87e22","tid":411173,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241227b79ab78c4b9f5c6f87482dbc45fd3caf96","tid":411173,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37374904a90740ae5783a636978f368107c